b0a617d617","tid":1613761,"uid":326282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2506325d02252fc65dfa92d925a6bd131c779edc","tid":1613761,"uid":141400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:26:16.000Z","msg":"根據POPO入職標準，<br />\n最小要有呢個數，<br />\n唔係邊度跑得贏popo呀！<br />\n<strong>POPO測試項目</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/15_recruit/fitness.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Fppp_tc%2F15_recruit%2Ffitness.html&d=Bbcm6JBZsUbsJrWfDZmHXw2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=4f9b0157\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/15_recruit/fitness.html</a><br />\n800米跑:  3 分 11 秒<br />\n4 x 10米穿梭跑: 10.92 秒<br />\n真香港人一齊全民跑online啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:13:31.000Z","msg":"中學學界成績參考<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X35PXst.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX35PXst.png&h=3901d27a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:16:09.000Z","msg":"女士要跑得贏男popo係有困難....."},{"pid":"8dd48f84a31555fffb0fd66304986dc8a02ae61c","tid":1613761,"uid":326282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db8a2d44df38c79800e21f5d142523f9326477ab","tid":1613761,"uid":279995,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:59:20.000Z","msg":"有冇話可以點練？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:34:14.000Z","msg":"去買隻計時手錶，例如garmin<br />\n落運動場，地上有段200米距離標誌<br />\n用自己60%氣力衝150米，邊行邊休息<br />\n先唔計跑步姿勢<br />\n試吓跑6次先<br />\n每星期跑兩晚<br />\n多多拉根及多多睡眠<br />\n<br />\n大約6個星期習慣左之後上70%力跑<br />\n想計成績就去衝4個1000米計時<br />\n<br />\n如果巴絲打衝1000米只需 2-4mins<br />\n<br />\n出去參加本地十公里賽事平均速度<br />\n成績算係中間水平了<br />\n<br />\n咁當然我地唔駛練十公里咁長氣袋<br />\n頂多當跑1500米比賽都夠做"}]}